<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

  <ShortName>MODAPS Dataset Search</ShortName>
  <Description>Use MODAPS Dataset Search to obtain a list of Earth Science Data Sets</Description>

  <Contact>MODAPSUSO@lists.nasa.gov</Contact>
